hopobject.body: Photography rizer xl australia TOKYO, Sept 18 (Reuters) - Toyota Motor Corp willinvest around 18 billion yen ($181 million) to expand capacityat its St. Petersburg plant in Russia where it will startassembling its popular RAV4 SUV in 2016, the Japanese carmakersaid on Wednesday. While car sales have been declining for six consecutivemonths in Europe's second biggest market due to an economicslowdown, Toyota has seen sales of the RAV4 rise by 43 percentto 27,000 vehicles in the eight months to August.
